There are 12.3 million people in the UK at increased risk of developing type 2
diabetes. But there are simple things you can do to change this.
That's why we're raising awareness of the risk of developing type 2 and how to
The first step is finding out whether you're at risk. It takes two minutes and
could be the most important thing you do today.
We're working hard to raise awareness, fund ground-breaking research and
campaign to create a more healthier environment. Find out how.
